Dialogue: 100,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.31,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Înțeleg...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:03.31,0:00:06.82,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Deci poți rămâne pe insula \NItogami fără să-ți faci griji, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.82,0:00:08.12,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Asta e grozav, Yume.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.52,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.77,0:00:12.54,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,Și mulțumită băiatului \Nnepoliticos de colo,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:12.54,0:00:15.73,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,am și pe cineva care \Nsă aibă grijă de mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.73,0:00:16.57,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.84,0:00:18.58,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,Deci, așteaptă-mă, bine?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.72,0:00:21.04,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Ce? Pentru ce să te aștept?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.72,0:00:25.84,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,Mi-ai... promis, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.84,0:00:29.87,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,Că mă vei face fericită \Npentru tot restul vieții...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.87,0:00:32.06,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,Voi da tot ce pot în tot ce voi face!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.52,0:00:37.03,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Stai, nu la asta mă refeream prin...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.03,0:00:39.18,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,Ce? Nu vorbeai serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.78,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,Dle polițist! Avem un escroc aici!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.78,0:00:43.26,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hei! Yaze!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.79,0:00:45.44,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Doamne... Ce naiba face?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.61,0:00:48.61,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Dar tu, Yukina? \NCe încerci să {\i1}faci{\i0}?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.16,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Dacă vrei să-i spui ceva lui Kojou,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.16,0:00:54.24,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,doar mergi la el și spune-i.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:55.01,0:00:58.74,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Dar nu pot da busna pur \Nși simplu în restaurant...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.89,0:01:00.28,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,De ce nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.09,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I don't think that's \Nanything to worry about.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.37,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Do you, Kanon-chan?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.92,0:01:09.85,Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,I... sort of understand \Nhow Yukina-chan feels.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.85,0:01:11.07,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.07,0:01:12.80,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,I mean, that's fine, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.80,0:01:15.51,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,E destul de amuzant să \Nte văd astfel, Yukina.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.71,0:01:17.19,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Ei bine...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.19,0:01:20.77,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Îmi cer scuze că v-am implicat în asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.77,0:01:22.20,Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,E în regulă.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.20,0:01:28.73,Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Mereu mi s-a părut distractiv \Nsă-i privesc împreună astfel.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.73,0:01:31.02,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Vai, e așa de cald.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.88,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Voi merge să-mi iau ceva de băut.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.88,0:01:35.31,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Vino cu mine, Kanon.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.31,0:01:36.99,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Tu vrei ceva, Yukina?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.99,0:01:40.30,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Ei bine... Eu vreau un ceai verde cu gheață.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.04,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Bine, am înțeles!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.91,0:01:49.92,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Excuse me, little miss middle schooler.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.13,0:01:54.26,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Banca aceea este liberă?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.65,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Oh, da, este. Vă puteți așeza.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.78,0:01:57.91,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Mulțumesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.91,0:01:59.88,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Vai, ce bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.48,0:02:07.44,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,So, what is a middle school girl \Nlike you to Akatsuki Kojou, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.54,0:02:08.39,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Poftim?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.39,0:02:13.12,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Well, you've been giving \NKojou a hell of a death glare.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.12,0:02:18.06,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,I thought maybe you were... \Nyou know, jealous or something.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.07,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Am dreptate?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.74,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Nu!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.74,0:02:25.59,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,D-Doar îl supraveghez! \NNu sunt geloasă deloc!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.01,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Supraveghezi... Supraveghezi, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.01,0:02:32.79,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Is that what you call \Nstalking a one-sided crush?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.79,0:02:33.80,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Poftim?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.87,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,"Observing"! I love it! \NAh, to be young again!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.87,0:02:39.23,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Damn, that's so bittersweet!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.23,0:02:41.41,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Why are we even discussing this?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.41,0:02:44.10,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Actually, first of all, who {\i1}are{\i0} you?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.82,Dialogue,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Gajou?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.10,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Oh, hei, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.69,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Chiar ești tu!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.60,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Ce cauți aici, tată oribil ce ești?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.72,0:02:55.20,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Tată?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.81,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,S-Sunteți tatăl...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.62,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,lui Akatsuki?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.39,0:03:07.60,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Eu sunt tatăl lui Kojou și \NNagisa, Akatsuki Gajou.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.95,Dialogue,Gajou,0,0,0,,Încântat de cunoștință.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.01,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,E așa de cald...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.09,0:04:45.50,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hey, Natsuki-chan, today—ow!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.45,0:04:52.85,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't call your teacher "chan" when she's \Nalready irritable from this stinking heat, idiot.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.30,0:04:58.67,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Today is New Year's Eve, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.20,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yes, that it is.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.20,0:05:04.36,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,So why am I stuck here taking \Nsupplementary lessons right now?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.36,0:05:10.17,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ask a certain idiot who failed his \Nmake-up exam due to his unexcused absence.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.72,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Astarte.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.72,0:05:12.92,Dialogue,Astarte,0,0,0,,Accept.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.63,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Are you being snarky?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.61,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,By the way, Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.66,0:05:22.31,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Where is your father right now?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.41,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,He's not on Itogami Island.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.41,0:05:26.32,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I mean, not that he ever is,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.32,0:05:29.38,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,but right now, he's visiting \Nthe mainland with my sister.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.38,0:05:30.26,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.38,0:05:33.92,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Well, actually, about... a week ago?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.92,0:05:36.16,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,He just suddenly showed up
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.16,0:05:39.14,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,and said he was taking Nagisa \Nto see our grandma in Tanzawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.40,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Tanzawa... hmm...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.62,0:05:43.73,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.67,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hang on, Natsuki-chan... \NDo you know my dad?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.28,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Unfortunately.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.95,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Akatsuki Gajou made \Na nuisance of himself many times
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.94,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,while I was working my other job.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.61,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He did come in handy \Non rare occasions, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.60,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Your attack mage job?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.67,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,What the hell was that old jerk doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.42,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Can you contact him?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.68,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.33,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,The area around Lake Kannawa,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.76,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,where my grandma lives, \Nhas really spotty cell service.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.94,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why do you ask, though?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.44,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Did you have business with him?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.87,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, I was just a bit curious,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.20,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,for whatever reason.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.81,0:06:25.84,Dialogue,Astarte,0,0,0,,We are aliens...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.45,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.63,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.49,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I'm leaving a change of clothes here. \NThey're Nagisa's, but they should work.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.50,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.72,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Thank you for letting me use the bath.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.28,0:06:49.57,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you help \Nwith the end-of-the-year cleaning.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.57,0:06:50.80,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Well, I had to.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.72,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,If you'd been left to do it all alone,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.52,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,it wouldn't have been done \Nbefore the year ended.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.52,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Damn it. What was my stupid mother thinking,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.52,0:07:02.02,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,with her "If you want New Year's money, \Nyou gotta clean! Hee hee!" line?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.99,0:07:07.15,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's not like she cares about New Year's. \NShe works through it like every other day.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.28,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'll get the New Year's soba ready.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.71,0:07:13.42,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,You can have your bath in the meantime.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.34,0:07:20.88,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Minamiya-sensei said that?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.20,0:07:25.38,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Yeah. She seemed concerned \Nabout my dad and Nagisa.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.68,0:07:30.08,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it's been \Na week now since they left.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.90,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Have you heard anything from Nagisa-chan?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.90,0:07:33.85,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.17,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,You haven't, either?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.51,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.51,0:07:40.70,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I see... Not even a word to you...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.99,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,Hey, Kojou. I came to see ya.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.88,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,What're you doing here at this hour?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.32,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.22,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,We said we'd all do the first \Nshrine visit of the year together.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.71,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Crap! Sorry, I totally forgot!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.25,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.79,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,They should be here soon.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.05,0:08:00.82,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.00,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,What are you guys wearing?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.84,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,W-Well, it's New Year's.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.69,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,We thought it'd be nice \Nto dress up for a change.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.36,0:08:28.65,Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Do we look okay, Onii-san?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.72,0:08:32.37,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,But it's crazy to wear long sleeves like \Nthat in this island's climate!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.23,0:08:33.40,Dialogue,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs36\c&H6D4F46&\3c&H411809&\shad0\frx14\fry20\frz352.1\fscy140\fay.01\move(735,30,735,264)}Current Temperature
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.40,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.50,0:08:36.56,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,W-We're fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.87,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,As long as we can get some water...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.34,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Here's some water for everyone. \NPlease help yourselves.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.81,Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Yukina-chan?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.81,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Fitting in quite naturally \Nat Kojou's place, aren't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.95,0:08:55.16,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Oh, um... Nagisa-chan \Nis away visiting family,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.16,0:08:58.69,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,so I was helping with his end-of-the-year \Ncleaning and New Year's soba.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.38,0:09:09.90,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,Look at you two, fresh out of the bath \Nand smelling like the same shampoo...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.63,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,Wait! You didn't actually get in together—
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.12,0:09:14.48,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,The hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.07,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,There's a child here!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.53,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,Man, that hurt!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.34,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,It was just a little joke to lighten things up!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.34,0:09:22.65,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.94,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi and I are gonna get ready now,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.94,0:09:26.30,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,so sit tight for a bit.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.23,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh, right... The air conditioner...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.64,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I just turned it down.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.89,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Thanks, Himeragi.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.46,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,They're just like newlyweds.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.46,0:09:39.17,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Motoki, this heat is making me \Nirritable enough as it is.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.89,Dialogue,Yaze,0,0,0,,Why don't ya go to his room \Nto change with him, then?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.09,0:09:49.08,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's from Nagisa. She finally—
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.83,0:09:50.77,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.38,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,A magic circle?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.52,Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.49,Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.64,0:10:01.45,Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.73,0:10:04.43,Dialogue,All,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.38,Dialogue,Guy,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.59,Dialogue,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.02,0:10:12.13,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Hey, Kojou, why are you making that face?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.13,0:10:15.29,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,We don't know for sure \Nthat anything happened to Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.83,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I know! I'm not worried or anything!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.51,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.51,0:10:25.72,Dialogue,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs42\move(1134,360,972,660)\c&H19E1E2&\3c&H091616&\shad0}Itogami Shrine\N{\c&H67AAE7&\3c&HDBF4FF&}Happy New Year
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.99,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Well, go ahead and say a prayer.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.44,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,They say prayers offered \Nat this shrine are granted.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.98,Dialogue,Text,0,0,0,,{\frx4\fry350\fs90\b1\c&H293235&\bord0\shad0\fay-.08\pos(975.999,726)}Fortunes
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.51,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,One more try!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.64,Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,Onii-san...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.63,Dialogue,Yume,0,0,0,,Want to trade for mine?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.55,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I-It's fine!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.55,0:10:56.23,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,If you're at your lowest now, \Nthat means it can't get any worse!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.23,0:11:01.14,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Yeah. Maybe the unluckier you are, \Nthe luckier Nagisa-chan will be!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.15,0:11:08.56,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,She's not gonna end up telling us this \Nwas just fireworks, is she?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.56,0:11:11.15,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,I really doubt that,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:11.15,0:11:14.57,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,but digital data can be \Naltered in all sorts of ways.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.97,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,You shouldn't dwell on it so much.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.65,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hey, Himeragi...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:21.14,0:11:23.23,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,If this is a magic circle,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.23,0:11:25.98,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,do you know what kind \Nof effect this type would have?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.98,0:11:30.16,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Sayaka-san might \Nknow, but I can't say I do.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.62,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Kirasaka?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:32.88,0:11:35.04,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Actually, this does look like...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.59,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,...Sayaka-san's Koukarin, yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.82,0:11:41.75,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Is there anyone else \Nwho has a bow like that?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.22,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,No, they're difficult to use.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.22,0:11:47.71,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I've heard Sayaka-san \Nis the only one who's mastered it.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:48.37,0:11:48.95,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.46,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I've also heard that there is \Na mass-produced model
Dialogue: 100,0:11:51.46,0:11:55.33,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,that's been simplified \Nto make it easier to use.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.76,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,It's only a rumor, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.08,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I'll ask her myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.92,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Who's he calling?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.50,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Sayaka-san.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.96,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,She knows a lot about \Nthat type of magic circle.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.84,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,How does he know Kirasaka-san's number?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.04,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:12.51,0:12:13.79,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,She's not answering.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.88,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,In fact, it's telling me \Nthis number isn't in use.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.81,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Then Sayaka-san's cell phone—
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.14,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hey, Himeragi!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.98,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Is there any other way \Nto get in touch with her?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.08,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.93,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,I know you're worried about Nagisa-chan,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.94,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,but don't grab a girl like that!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:29.19,0:12:31.49,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Sorry, Himeragi. I wasn't thinking.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:31.49,0:12:32.73,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.73,0:12:35.52,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Nagisa-chan, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:37.28,0:12:39.17,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.45,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.68,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,L-Listen, Kojou...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.29,0:12:48.64,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,My parents are out tonight, \Nso no one's home.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.75,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Want to come over?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.68,0:12:58.30,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.92,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,There! That's Nagisa-chan \Nand your dad, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.68,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,The security cameras, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.43,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I get it. \NThis'll tell us where they're going.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:12.43,0:13:18.27,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Right, yes... Of course this \Nis what she meant.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.03,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:19.03,0:13:21.34,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Nothing! Never mind!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.29,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Her dad rented a car at the airport...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.23,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,using an alias.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.12,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why an alias?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.20,Dialogue,ASagi,0,0,0,,The car left Haneda on the Metropolitan \NExpressway, bound for Tokyo...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.72,0:13:35.13,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,But they stopped briefly \Njust before Shibuya.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.13,0:13:36.23,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Shibuya?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.97,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,There's a record of them shopping \Nat a second-hand clothes shop in Harajuku.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.44,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,They also stopped to eat cake.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.63,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Then they checked into a hotel, and...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.93,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,What is this place? A strip bar?!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.14,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Wait, with Nagisa?!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:49.38,0:13:50.96,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,No, he's alone.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.61,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,That piece of shit!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.77,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,They spent the next day \Nat an amusement park,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.36,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,and they booked a hotel on the grounds.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:58.36,0:14:01.32,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Is there any point in tracing all this stuff?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.32,0:14:05.28,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Oh, it looks like they finally \Ngot serious the next day.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.80,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Finally?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:06.80,0:14:10.04,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,The date matches the one \Non Nagisa-chan's message.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.02,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.66,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Do you see it, Mogwai?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.56,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:14.56,0:14:16.24,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Weird? What's weird?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.09,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,They're moving around too smoothly.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.09,0:14:23.52,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,It's New Year's, and they haven't \Ngotten caught in traffic once.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:23.52,0:14:27.51,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,It's almost as if all the other cars \Nare avoiding the route to Kannawa.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.92,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Couldn't it just be a coincidence?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.98,StB_Italics,Yukina,0,0,0,,Did someone put up \Na barrier to repel people?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.22,0:14:38.21,StB_Italics,Yukina,0,0,0,,But it would take a major organized effort \Nto put up a barrier on this scale.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.42,0:14:41.12,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,I get it. I figured out the trick.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.14,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,The Self-Defense Force is behind it.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.63,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,They're heading toward Kannawa Lake \Nunder the pretense of offering aid
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.42,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,in the wake of snowfall and landslides.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.61,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,The Self-Defense Force?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:48.80,0:14:52.86,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,But the group that's really \Npulling the strings is SDC,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.86,0:14:55.12,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,also known as Sorcery Disaster Control.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.64,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,SDC?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:57.57,0:14:59.80,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,No... But why...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:59.80,0:15:00.59,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.89,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.39,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.28,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hey, Himeragi! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.19,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Wait, Kojou!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.64,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Thanks, Asagi! You were a big help! \NI owe you dinner or something!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.65,0:15:19.07,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Jeez, what's going on?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:20.40,0:15:23.02,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Hey, Himeragi! What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.32,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:25.31,0:15:27.49,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I need to know for sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.76,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Know what for sure?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:29.76,0:15:35.42,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,SDC is one of the dummy organizations \Nunder the Lion King Organization.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:35.82,0:15:37.74,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,The Lion King Organization?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:37.74,0:15:41.63,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,What's this about? It's called \NSorcery Disaster Control, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.63,0:15:45.43,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,So does that mean Nagisa \Nwas involved in a magic-related disaster?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.87,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Or they involved her in one...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.52,0:15:50.85,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Which is why I need to go find out for sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.47,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,At that antique shop?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.39,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,The one where Cat-sensei \Nand that Kirasaka puppet were?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.56,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I thought it was in this area...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.56,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,The barrier spell has changed.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.99,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Even I can't decode it now.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.74,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,If that's what they want...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.31,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Himeragi?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.33,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, please stay back here.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.90,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Schneesturm Wolfin!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.99,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,That was a bit overboard...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.46,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.46,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Looks like the shop's closed.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.46,0:16:35.39,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I guess it would be, since it's New Year's.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.53,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Whoa, Himeragi!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.53,0:16:46.85,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Don't try to stop me!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.25,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Forget it! Just calm down!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.18,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:49.18,0:16:52.15,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,There's no point in going inside \Nwhen no one's in there!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.15,0:16:53.15,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:53.15,0:16:56.03,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,If no one has told you anything,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.03,0:17:00.27,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,that must mean the Lion King Organization \Nis deliberately keeping us out of the loop.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.74,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,That would explain Kirasaka's deal, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.21,0:17:06.49,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,How can you be so calm right now?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.59,0:17:10.93,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,The Lion King Organization may have \Ninvolved Nagisa-chan in something terrible!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.27,0:17:14.06,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say I'm all that calm.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.06,0:17:14.96,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.44,0:17:20.43,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Organizations always have different \Nfactions vying for all the power.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:20.43,0:17:24.56,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,So if there's a side to the Lion \NKing Organization that you don't know,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.98,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,it's nothing you need \Nto feel responsible for.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.48,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:28.66,0:17:33.11,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Besides, there's no way \NKirasaka would ever betray you.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.64,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.64,0:17:40.53,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I understand... so, Senpai...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.53,0:17:44.08,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you'd let go of me now.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.30,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're touching, anyway?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.76,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:47.76,0:17:52.42,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. It was \Nmy fault to begin with.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.94,0:17:57.32,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,But I guess we still don't know what \Nthe Lion King Organization's up to, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.88,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,So we're stuck.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.88,0:18:01.44,Dialogue,Kiriha,0,0,0,,You seem troubled, Fourth Progenitor.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.36,0:18:04.85,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Kisaki Kiriha!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.20,Dialogue,Kiriha,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.57,Dialogue,Kiriha,0,0,0,,when you were so boldly embracing \Non a street filled with love hotels
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.19,Dialogue,Kiriha,0,0,0,,on the first day of the new year.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.93,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Wha— I-It's not like that!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.93,0:18:14.59,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,We weren't embracing!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.84,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,What the hell do you want with us, anyway?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.63,Dialogue,Kiriha,0,0,0,,You want to know what
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.63,0:18:23.37,Dialogue,Kiriha,0,0,0,,the Lion King Organization \Nis doing at Lake Kannawa, don't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.83,Dialogue,Kiriha,0,0,0,,I'm willing to tell you.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.12,0:18:32.83,Dialogue,Kiriha,0,0,0,,Of course, once you find out, \Nyou may regret it.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.06,Dialogue,Nurse,0,0,0,,Okay, this will sting a little.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.62,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,It's such a hassle going \Nthrough this every time.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.97,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,I know it's necessary, \Nsince we're in a demon district, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:51.24,0:18:52.96,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,You're one brave little miss,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.08,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,going all the way to \Nthe mainland to help Kojou out.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:57.08,0:18:59.72,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,I'm not doing it for him, okay?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:59.72,0:19:02.95,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,My sister's on the mainland, \Nand I want to see her again, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.34,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd check \Nin on Nagisa-chan while I'm there.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.09,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:06.09,0:19:08.58,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Just shut up, would you?! It's time to go!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.62,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Gate 4, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.52,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,We've got trouble. It's the Island Guard.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:13.71,0:19:14.66,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:14.66,0:19:16.76,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,They're after you, without a doubt.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.83,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,You'll be fully surrounded \Nin one minute and forty seconds.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.93,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:21.93,0:19:25.36,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,You can get out to the taxiway \Nvia a staircase sixty meters ahead.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.61,StB_Italics,Mogwai,0,0,0,,Then it's all up to luck.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:26.68,0:19:30.82,Dialogue,Asagi,0,0,0,,Damn it! Why is this happening \Non the first day of the new year?!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:31.62,0:19:34.60,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're sure you want to go with me?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.90,0:19:37.81,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,I'm your observer, remember?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:38.14,0:19:43.06,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,If you're leaving the island via illegal means \Nwith help from Minamiya-sensei,
Dialogue: 100,0:19:43.06,0:19:45.25,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,of course I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.09,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,We'll be committing a crime, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.61,0:19:50.08,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,You're pointing that out {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.34,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.08,0:19:59.76,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Asagi's house is huge, \Ntoo, but this is crazy.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.60,Dialogue,Astarte,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:04.83,0:20:07.13,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,We already went through \Nthe New Year formalities!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:07.13,0:20:08.35,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,And why are you naked?!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:08.35,0:20:11.81,Dialogue,Kanon,0,0,0,,No, Astarte-san! \NYou shouldn't run around like that!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.48,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.10,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,W-Were you in the bath?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:23.10,0:20:25.82,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,How long do you have to stare at them?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:26.13,0:20:28.96,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai, you are such...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.31,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,an indecent person!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.29,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.64,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Barging into someone's home
Dialogue: 100,0:20:36.64,0:20:39.71,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and making a molester of yourself \Non the first day of the new year?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.00,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're still on my case about that?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.80,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I think I've more than paid my dues already.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.97,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What else are you here for, then?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.97,0:20:50.33,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,To hound me for New Year's money?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.48,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,You're close.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:52.82,0:20:55.72,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,I want to go to the mainland. Help me out.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.39,0:21:01.67,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Then you need to go to \Nthe appropriate office and get a visa.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.86,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But you'll need to be registered \Nas a demon before it'll be approved,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.54,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,which would expose your identity.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.78,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,That's why I came to ask you for help.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:09.78,0:21:14.54,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,It'd be easy for you to get me off the island \Nwithout all the inspections, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.37,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Even if I could do that,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:18.37,0:21:21.70,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I don't see why I'm obligated \Nto do that for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:21.70,0:21:24.00,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Even if I told you \Nsomeone's life depends on it?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:25.42,0:21:28.66,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't go poking around in the \NLake Kannawa matter, Akatsuki Kojou.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:29.36,0:21:32.15,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No matter how much you're \Nworried about your sister.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:32.55,0:21:34.14,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,You know about it?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.82,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Then please, Natsuki-chan! \NYou have to help me!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:36.82,0:21:37.85,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.36,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:40.25,0:21:44.00,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Do I need a reason to stop my student \Nfrom breaking the law?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.20,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Fine. I get it.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.43,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.36,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,It's okay, Natsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:53.36,0:21:57.16,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Sorry to ask that of you \Nwithout considering your position.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.20,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:00.20,0:22:02.99,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hold it, Akatsuki. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:04.37,0:22:05.56,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,To ask someone else.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:05.56,0:22:06.40,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:22.24,0:22:23.54,Dialogue,Kojou,0,0,0,,Natsuki-chan!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:23.75,0:22:28.40,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How many times must I tell you not to \Naddress your teacher with "chan"?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:30.12,0:22:31.09,Dialogue,Yukina,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:32.56,0:22:34.05,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Akatsuki Kojou...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:34.48,0:22:37.30,Dialogue,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to get to the mainland.
